         OpenTelemetry.* (via Altinn.Authorization.ServiceDefaults): GHSA-q834-8qmm-v933, GHSA-mr8r-92fq-pj8p, GHSA-4625-4j76-fww9, GHSA-g94r-2vxg-569j.
